| `eu-brg` | EU Better Regulation (evaluation and impact assessment) | Maps to Five Case: Strategic ≈ Context and Problem Definition; Economic ≈ Impact Assessment; Commercial ≈ Implementation; Financial ≈ Budgetary Impact; Management ≈ Monitoring and Review | 3% advanced / 5% convergence | Scenario sensitivity |
| `wb` | World Bank Project Appraisal Document (PAD) | Maps to Five Case: Strategic ≈ Country Partnership Framework alignment; Economic ≈ Economic and Financial Analysis; Commercial ≈ Procurement; Financial ≈ Financial Management; Management ≈ Implementation Arrangements | Country-specific ERR (typically 6%) | Scenario sensitivity |
| `adb` | Asian Development Bank Report and Recommendation of the President (RRP) | Maps to Five Case: Strategic ≈ Country Operations Business Plan alignment; Economic ≈ Economic Analysis; Commercial ≈ Procurement; Financial ≈ Financial Management; Management ≈ Implementation Arrangements | 9% EIRR (6% for climate / health / education) | Scenario sensitivity + switching values |
